('> [!WARNING]
> **¡¡CUIDADO CON LOS TRADUCTORES JURADOS!!**
> Hay traductores que ofrecen precios bajos pero **NO** están reconocidos en España. Puede que sean traductores jurados en su país de origen, pero eso no vale. **VERIFICA:**
> - Entra en Google y busca **"lista de traductores jurados"** del Ministerio de Asuntos Exteriores de España.
> - Comprueba que la persona está en esa lista **antes de pagar**.

**Validez de los antecedentes penales:**
- Si tu país de origen **NO** especifica validez, España les da una validez de **6 MESES**.
- Si tu país de origen **SÍ** especifica una validez (por ejemplo, 90 días), se aplica la del país de origen.
- Dado que el plazo de presentación es abril-junio (3 meses), en principio los 6 meses de validez no deberían vencer.
- Si los antecedentes tienen validez de 90 días y los metes antes de que caduquen, quedan registrados. Si después te requieren algo, se verá en ese momento. La recomendación es presentarlos **ANTES** de que venzan.', '[-0.0012142907,0.0006110538,0.022321118,-0.021152044,-0.0010369469,0.020394417,0.024977941,-0.008562704,-0.0059690024,-0.0022177165,0.0016375225,0.035339702,0.030255549,-0.006342341,0.14853404,0.023401976,0.0091046,0.0011262503,-0.007051454,-0.010694918,0.013016509,0.0066182287,-0.00804138,-0.0012325104,-0.01213589,0.0031898266,0.018047122,-0.00069071236,0.031099977,0.015542381,0.00021274827,0.018919323,-0.012293323,0.0047527757,-0.02669174,0.008205446,0.007974042,-0.0069229873,0.0063637667,0.013452978,0.009656731,0.026027132,-0.00832641,-0.0068165967,-0.01102864,-0.0053158165,0.0102214785,-0.00091473665,-0.0054954216,0.026351552,0.0012859371,-0.014106899,-0.037624262,-0.17272992,-0.028672442,-0.015004392,-0.0047164173,-0.008632322,0.009187592,-0.023428813,-0.030811934,0.046719536,-0.015636222,-0.0030028445,0.0044563566,-1.3816724e-05,-0.03853557,0.01857597,-0.024020426,-0.0074676583,0.008184707,-0.014157417,0.018398771,-0.024652088,0.034018528,-0.008344578,0.022756161,0.004737186,0.0022890004,-0.027130106,-0.013662484,0.008943388,-0.0074506835,-0.01064102,-0.0013093314,-0.010602711,-0.0028888304,0.029617868,-0.0011230479,0.030502073,-0.019866815,-0.008206336,0.0020138654,0.009203451,0.008678625,-0.004304665,0.0037761794,0.016246647,-0.005889363,-0.033556495,-0.007283491,-0.011238418,-0.002468049,0.008134266,0.03599044,-0.0040146546,-0.024319427,0.017177446,-0.010059478,0.014745072,0.00429567,0.00411291,-0.019294685,0.029703358,0.016599393,-0.12562254,0.0054130713,0.007881094,-0.03440299,-0.003767291,0.0041233255,0.008946114,0.013054064,0.01798789,-0.0058723064,-0.009032952,0.021451762,-0.0033931416,-0.010541971,-0.02531834,0.011335834,-0.0023998462,0.035393327,-0.00047176357,0.008923687,-0.0149862645,-0.027759487,-0.015327369,0.023628268,-0.0048621064